            <p>Hello, <strong>{email.split('@')[0]}</strong>,</p>
            <p>Your order has been placed and is being processed today with an amount of <strong>${amount} USD</strong> scheduled to be debited from your account. Please note that this amount will appear on your account statement within the next 24 hours.</p>
